l enable` — sets `strategy_options.trails = true` (or removes the key since true is default). Saves to project settings.\\n\\n`entire trail disable` — sets `strategy_options.trails = false`. Saves to local settings by default, `--project` flag for project settings.\\n\\nFollow the pattern from `setup.go` `runEnable`/`runDisable` — load settings, modify `StrategyOptions`, save.\\n\\n### 3. Guard auto-create with settings check\\n**File**: `cmd/entire/cli/lifecycle.go` — `autoCreateTrailOnTurnStart()`\\n\\nAdd at the top:\\n```go\\nif settings.IsTrailsDisabled() {\\n    return\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 4. Guard push with settings check\\n**File**: `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/push_common.go` — `PushTrailsBranch()`\\n\\nAdd check:\\n```go\\nfunc PushTrailsBranch(remote string) error {\\n    if isTrailsDisabled() { return nil }\\n    return pushSessionsBranchCommon(remote, paths.TrailsBranchName)\\n}\\n```\\n\\nWhere `isTrailsDisabled()` loads settings (same pattern as `isPushSessionsDisabled()`).\\n\\n### 5. Update CLAUDE.md\\nDocument the enable/disable commands and settings key.\\n\\n## Files Summary\\n\\n| File | Change |\\n|------|--------|\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/settings/settings.go` | Add `IsTrailsDisabled()` method + package-level function |\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/trail_cmd.go` | Add `newTrailEnableCmd()`, `newTrailDisableCmd()` |\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/lifecycle.go` | Guard `autoCreateTrailOnTurnStart()` with settings check |\\n| `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/push_common.go` | Guard `PushTrailsBranch()` with settings check |\\n| `CLAUDE.md` | Document enable/disable |\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n```bash\\nmise run fmt && mise run lint && mise run test:ci\\n```\\n\\nManual: `entire trail disable` then verify no trail auto-created on session start.\\n\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":3992,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":159201,\"output_tokens\":1017,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_r